<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>LAS 3.0 - Draw Art Daily</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-dark" style="background: coral;">
	<button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#nav-content" aria-controls="nav-content" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
	<span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
	</button>

	<!-- Brand -->
	<a class="navbar-brand" href="/">DAD</a>
	
	
	<div id="navbarNavDropdown" class="navbar-collapse collapse">
            <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
                <li class="nav-item active">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            
            <ul class=" navbar-nav">
              <li><a class="nav-link" href="/signup"><span class="fa fa-edit"></span> Sign Up</a></li>
              <li><a class="nav-link" href="/login"><span class="fa fa-external-link"></span> Login</a></li>
            </ul>
    </div>
	</nav>
	</div>
        <div class="center jumbotron">
          <h1>Welcome to Draw Art Daily!</h1>
        
          <h2>
            This is the home page for the website. Still in progress!
          </h2>
        
          <%= link_to "Sign up now!", signup_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
        </div>
  
  <div class="row">
	    <div class="col-sm-6">
	      <div id="websiteProgressContent" class="collapse show" role="tabcard" aria-labelledby="websiteProgress">
                	<div class="card-body">
                	    <p>the1banana and NicNac are working together to make the third iteration of LAS. Where LAS and DED have fallen, we hope that this will become the permanent home for the journeys of aspiring artists.</p>
                	    <div class="progress">
                	        <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="15" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 5%"></div>
                	    </div>
                	   <br>
                <b>15% Complete</b>
                <p>Done: 1. Domain name and hosting server purchased. 
                <br>2. Signups finished. 
                <br>Next: Start building Login!</p>
                </div>
        	</div>
        	
        	</div>
    	</div>
